name: 1.4ct Oval Teal Sapphire and Recycled Silver ring
description:
Recycled silver ring with a gorgeous oval, teal Malawi Sapphire horizontally set in a tapered setting.

The Sapphire is Fair Trade and Fair Mined, allowing safe and ethical practice for small-scale miners.

The ring is comfort-fit (rounded on the inside for comfortable wear) and is textured all the way around with a dappled effect, which catches the light.

This ring is a size M.

name: 0.5ct Teal Sapphire and Recycled Silver Ring
description:
Recycled 925 sterling silver ring with a gorgeous teal Malawi Sapphire set in a tapered setting.

The Sapphire is Fair Trade and Fair Mined, allowing safe and ethical practice for small-scale miners.

The ring is textured all the way around with a fine, beaten effect and is made from a slightly chunkier 2.5cm square wire.

This ring is fully hallmarked.

If your size is not available a ring can be custom made at no extra charge. Colour of Sapphire may vary depending on availability. Please allow 3-5 days for non-hallmarked custom made items and up to 2 weeks for items requiring to be hallmarked.

description:

The pendant is on a gorgeous, lightweight 16 inch rope chain. The pendant is secured from the back, giving the illusion of the pendant sitting on the chain at the collarbone.
